  <h1>Kansas Local Sales Tax Calculator</h1>
<div class="container">
<p>This calculator is designed to help residents and businesses in Kansas quickly and accurately calculate the local sales tax due on a purchase. By inputting the purchase amount and selecting the applicable tax rate, you can easily determine the total tax payable.</p>
<div class="calculator-layout">
<section aria-labelledby="calculator-heading" class="calculator-container">
<h2 id="calculator-heading">Sales Tax Calculator</h2>
<div class="form-group">
<label for="purchaseAmount">Purchase Amount ($) *</label>
<input aria-describedby="purchaseAmountError" aria-required="true" class="form-control" id="purchaseAmount" type="number">
<div aria-live="polite" class="error-message" id="purchaseAmountError" role="alert"></div>
</div>
<div class="form-group">
<label for="taxRate">Tax Rate (%) *</label>
<input aria-describedby="taxRateError" aria-required="true" class="form-control" id="taxRate" type="number">
